Company Overview of New England Research & Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
New England Research & Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides retirement strategies, tax planning, cash flow analysis, and financial planning. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, families, firms, pension and profit sharing plans, and charitable organizations. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm employs a combination of in-house and external research to make its investments. New England Rese...
New England Research & Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm also provides retirement strategies, tax planning, cash flow analysis, and financial planning. It primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. The firm also caters to individuals, families, firms, pension and profit sharing plans, and charitable organizations. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm employs a combination of in-house and external research to make its investments. New England Research & Management, Inc. was founded in 1978 and is based in Chicago, Illinois with an additional office in Boston, Massachusetts.
