New England Research & Management, Inc. is a personalized, long-term investment management services firm with offices in Boston and Chicago. The firm was founded in 1978.

              At NERM, we are focused on building strong, lasting relationships with our clients and enhancing the performance of their assets over the long haul. We are proud to provide financial comfort to individuals, families, and firms across the country and around the world.


