“As a trusted adviser, I work hard to provide a highly personalized approach to wealth management. I’m proud to lead an organization that continually asks, ‘Is there anything else we can do for you?’, and look forward to building wonderful relationships with clients as we work to meet and exceed their long-term financial goals.” — Marguerite McMullen Collins











